Package org.hibernate.boot.jaxb.mapping

Interface LifecycleCallbackContainer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    EntityOrMappedSuperclass
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JaxbEntity, JaxbEntityListener, JaxbMappedSuperclass
    public interface LifecycleCallbackContainer
    JAXB binding interface for commonality between things which allow callback declarations. This includes
    • entities and mapped-superclasses
    • entity-listener classes
